OL,3,CMan caught with cocaine, ketamine and
OL,4,Ccannabis worth thousands
OL,6,FA Plymouth man who was caught with
OL,7,Fcocaine, ketamine and cannabis worth
OL,8,F#60,000 has been jailed.
OL,10,FRyan Board, 30, of Rochford Crescent
OL,11,Fhad previously pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fsupplying class A and B drugs and
OL,13,Fpossession of offensive weapons.
OL,15,FHe appeared at Plymouth Crown Court on
OL,16,FFriday, 12 June, and was sentenced to
OL,17,Ftwo years and eight months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
