CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781543166
OL,3,CMan caught with cocaine, ketamine and
OL,4,Ccannabis worth thousands
OL,6,FIt follows an investigation by the
OL,7,FSouth West Regional Organised Crime
OL,8,FUnit (SWROCU), supported by Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall Police.
OL,11,FWhen a warrant was executed at Board's
OL,12,Faddress, officers seized more than 530
OL,13,Fgrams of cocaine, 3.8 kilos of
OL,14,Fketamine, 245 grams of cannabis and
OL,15,F#34,660 in bundled cash.
OL,17,FBoard was sentenced to nearly three
OL,18,Fyears' imprisonment for:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
