OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781543166
OL,3,CMan caught with cocaine, ketamine and
OL,4,Ccannabis worth thousands
OL,6,FDI Pete Walker from SWROCU said: "The
OL,7,Fseizure of drugs with a potential
OL,8,Fstreet value of in excess of #60,000
OL,9,Falong with thousands of pounds in
OL,10,Fcash, demonstrates that Board was
OL,11,Fheavily involved in serious
OL,12,Fcriminality which causes real harm to
OL,13,Four communities.
OL,15,F"In addition, we recovered two weapons
OL,16,Fwhich show the very real threat
OL,17,Fcriminals involved in drug supply can
OL,18,Fpose.
OL,26,@nD@bOU
