OL,3,CMan caught with cocaine, ketamine and
OL,4,Ccannabis worth thousands
OL,6,F"People living in our towns who seek
OL,7,Fto profit from illegal activity can
OL,8,Fexpect to be pursued by the police and
OL,9,Fbrought before the court."
